---
// The Challenge section for CRE industry page
---

<section id="challenge" class="cre-challenge-section">
  <div class="cre-challenge-container">
    <span class="section-label">THE CHALLENGE</span>
    <h2 class="cre-challenge-headline">
      Speed vs. process in commercial real estate
    </h2>
    <p class="cre-challenge-subheadline">
      Commercial real estate moves fast. Deals appear and disappear in days. Investors need answers immediately. 
      But most CRE firms are still running on spreadsheets, manual processes, and disconnected systems that can't keep up.
    </p>

    <!-- Highlight Box -->
    <div class="cre-highlight-box">
      <p class="cre-highlight-text">
        "The average CRE firm misses 30-40% of qualified deals because they can't evaluate and respond fast enough."
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Challenge List -->
    <div class="cre-challenge-list-wrapper">
      <ul class="cre-challenge-list">
        <li><strong>Deal sourcing is fragmented</strong> across email, spreadsheets, and broker networks—making it impossible to track what's in your pipeline.</li>
        <li><strong>Underwriting takes too long</strong> because data lives in silos. Analysts spend hours copying numbers between systems instead of analyzing deals.</li>
        <li><strong>Portfolio performance is opaque</strong> because reporting requires manual data pulls from multiple sources, delaying critical decisions.</li>
        <li><strong>Investor reporting is reactive</strong> instead of proactive. You're building reports after questions are asked, not before they're needed.</li>
        <li><strong>Market intelligence is scattered</strong> across news feeds, broker updates, and internal notes—making it hard to spot opportunities.</li>
        <li><strong>Team coordination breaks down</strong> when deal information lives in email threads and shared drives instead of a single source of truth.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Stat Cards -->
    <div class="cre-stat-cards">
      <div class="cre-stat-card">
        <div class="cre-stat-number">30-40%</div>
        <div class="cre-stat-label">deals missed</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cre-stat-card">
        <div class="cre-stat-number">60+ hrs</div>
        <div class="cre-stat-label">per deal</div>
      </div>
      <div class="cre-stat-card">
        <div class="cre-stat-number">3-5 days</div>
        <div class="cre-stat-label">investor reporting</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cre-challenge-section {
    background: #FFFFFF;
    padding: clamp(50px, 6vw, 80px) 24px;
  }

  .cre-challenge-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cre-challenge-headline {
    font-family: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 52px);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #000000;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .cre-challenge-subheadline {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .cre-highlight-box {
    background: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.05);
    border-left: 4px solid #0EA5E9;
    padding: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .cre-highlight-text {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #000000;
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .cre-challenge-list-wrapper {
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .cre-challenge-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .cre-challenge-list li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 32px;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
  }

  .cre-challenge-list li::before {
    content: '−';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #0EA5E9;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .cre-challenge-list li strong {
    color: #000000;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .cre-stat-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .cre-stat-card {
    background: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.2);
    padding: 32px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
  }

  .cre-stat-card:hover {
    background: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1);
    border-color: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.4);
  }

  .cre-stat-number {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #0EA5E9;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .cre-stat-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    text-transform: lowercase;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .cre-challenge-list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cre-stat-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cre-challenge-section {
      padding: clamp(30px, 4vw, 50px) 24px;
    }

    .cre-highlight-box {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .cre-stat-card {
      padding: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>

